messages.message:
Day 1 of university workshops done in Chandigarh
• Intense engagement from 50+ teachers. Use cases: 
    ◦ each faculty has to create a question bank of 500 questions of varying difficulty each semester in every course 
    ◦ Translation of first information reports (criminal) from Hindi / Punjabi into English. 
    ◦ Translation and summarisation of court judgments
    ◦ Checking if student work is AI based or not 
• Medium level engagement from 200+ students.
    ◦ Students would like to see the mobile support asap! :slightly_smiling_face: 
    ◦ Most want help with solving assignments and question papers. 
    ◦ Most computer science faculty reported that they are already using AI tools for their work 
Day 2 with 2000 students and 100+ teachers tomorrow! We will share more details next week.

Instabase has arrived on campus — 2000 new AI Hub users await :grinning:
